snippet.title: How is the formulation of Qualia unique?
snippet.description:
Neurohacker.com
Daniel Schmachtenberger discusses what is unique about the formulation of Qualia, a broad spectrum cognitive enhancement nootropic stack.
Qualia is a general cognitive enhancement stack designed to amplify all the aspects that matter most for optimal cognitive and nervous system functioning.
For the full list of ingredients check out neurohacker.com/formulation

Qualia was designed to provide immediate, noticeable uplift of your subjective experience within 20 minutes of taking it, as well as long-term benefits to your neurology and overall physiologic functioning; this means supporting the functioning of the brain and the pathways of the central nervous system (neural, immune, endocrine), balancing hormones, improving biochemical signaling of the gut-brain axis, and supporting the core underlying regulatory mechanisms of the brain and body that give rise to our subjective experience.
http://neurohacker.com/qualia/
